        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer20565403" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5314957375160609825">In brief: No. This book doesn&apos;t do it. At all. At any time. I grudgingly give Lethem credit for trying to write the &quot;Great American Novel,&quot; but it comes off short and ends up being overtly pretentious. And I can&apos;t believe they still wheel this guy out at every literary event happening within 50 miles of Brooklyn. Stop! Please, stop! </span>
  <span id="freeText5314957375160609825" style="display:none">In brief: No. This book doesn't do it. At all. At any time. I grudgingly give Lethem credit for trying to write the "Great American Novel," but it comes off short and ends up being overtly pretentious. And I can't believe they still wheel this guy out at every literary event happening within 50 miles of Brooklyn. Stop! Please, stop! </span>
